Class BytesBytesMultiHashMap.Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.exec.persistence.BytesBytesMultiHashMap.Result

    BytesBytesMultiHashMap

    public static class BytesBytesMultiHashMap.Result
extends Object
    The result of looking up a key in the multi-hash map. This object can read through the 0, 1, or more values found for the key.

        Set internal values for reading the values after finding a key.
        Parameters:
        hashMap - The hash map we found the key in.
        firstOffset - The absolute offset of the first record in the write buffers.
        hasList - Whether there are multiple values (true) or just a single value (false).
        offsetAfterListRecordKeyLen - The offset of just after the key length in the list record. Or, 0 when single row.
